      "content": "That's a great start, really captures that condescending tone. Can you expand on it a bit? I want to lean more into his 'scientific' observations. Like, have him describe the physical differences or the perceived intellectual limitations he sees in them compared to Europeans, to justify why they need this 'guidance'. Just keep it in that 19th-century explorer voice.",
